{"data":[{"name":"102:1","price":"പരസ്പരം പെരുമ നടിക്കുക എന്ന കാര്യം നിങ്ങളെ അശ്രദ്ധയിലാക്കിയിരിക്കുന്നു.","arabic":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6169,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"alhākumu al-takāthuru ","translations":["Diverts you","the competition to increase","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["alhākumu","al-takāthuru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,3315]]}},{"name":"102:2","price":"നിങ്ങള്‍ ശവകുടീരങ്ങള്‍ സന്ദര്‍ശിക്കുന്നത് വരേക്കും.(1)","arabic":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6170,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1) 'നിങ്ങള്‍ ശവകുടീരങ്ങള്‍ സന്ദര്‍ശിക്കുന്നതുവരെ' എന്നതുകൊണ്ട് ഇവിടെ ഉദ്ദേശിക്കപ്പെട്ടത് 'നിങ്ങള്‍ മരിച്ച് മറവു ചെയ്യപ്പെടുന്നതുവരെ' എന്നത്രെ. ഭൗതികനേട്ടങ്ങളുടെ പേരിലുള്ള പെരുമയും പൊങ്ങച്ചവും കാരണം സത്യത്തെയും ധര്‍മത്തെയും പറ്റി മനുഷ്യര്‍ അശ്രദ്ധയിലാകുന്ന അവസ്ഥ മരണം വരെയും തുടരുന്നു എന്ന സത്യത്തിലേക്ക് ഈ വചനങ്ങള്‍ നമ്മുടെ ശ്രദ്ധ തിരിക്കുന്നു.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ḥattā zur'tumu al-maqābira ","translations":["Until","you visit","the graves","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["ḥattā","zur'tumu","al-maqābira",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,1800],[3,1800,3955]]}},{"name":"102:3","price":"നിസ്സംശയം, നിങ്ങള്‍ വഴിയെ അറിഞ്ഞു കൊള്ളും.","arabic":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6171,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā sawfa taʿlamūna ","translations":["Nay","Soon","you will know","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","sawfa","taʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1570],[3,1570,5275]]}},{"name":"102:4","price":"പിന്നെയും, നിസ്സംശയം നിങ്ങള്‍ വഴിയെ അറിഞ്ഞു കൊള്ളും.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6172,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma kallā sawfa taʿlamūna ","translations":["Then","nay","Soon","you will know","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","kallā","sawfa","taʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1620],[2,1620,2530],[3,2530,3320],[4,3320,6665]]}},{"name":"102:5","price":"നിസ്സംശയം, നിങ്ങള്‍ ദൃഢമായ അറിവ് അറിയുമായിരുന്നെങ്കില്‍.","arabic":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6173,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā law taʿlamūna ʿil'ma al-yaqīni ","translations":["Nay","If","you know","(with) a knowledge","(of) certainty","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","law","taʿlamūna","ʿil'ma","al-yaqīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,1270],[3,1270,2520],[4,2520,3140],[5,3140,6505]]}},{"name":"102:6","price":"ജ്വലിക്കുന്ന നരകത്തെ നിങ്ങള്‍ കാണുക തന്നെ ചെയ്യും.","arabic":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6174,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"latarawunna al-jaḥīma ","translations":["Surely you will see","the Hellfire","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["latarawunna","al-jaḥīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2230],[2,2230,5995]]}},{"name":"102:7","price":"പിന്നെ തീര്‍ച്ചയായും നിങ്ങള്‍ അതിനെ ദൃഢമായും കണ്ണാല്‍ കാണുക തന്നെ ചെയ്യും.","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6175,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma latarawunnahā ʿayna al-yaqīni ","translations":["Then","surely you will see it","(with the) eye","(of) certainty","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","latarawunnahā","ʿayna","al-yaqīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,3870],[3,3870,4450],[4,4450,7995]]}},{"name":"102:8","price":"പിന്നീട് ആ ദിവസത്തില്‍ സുഖാനുഭവങ്ങളെപ്പറ്റി തീര്‍ച്ചയായും നിങ്ങള്‍ ചോദ്യം ചെയ്യപ്പെടുക തന്നെ ചെയ്യും.(2)","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6176,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2) അല്ലാഹുവിന്റെ അളവറ്റ അനുഗ്രഹങ്ങള്‍ ആസ്വദിച്ചു കൊണ്ടാണ് ഓരോ നിമിഷവും നാം ജീവിക്കുന്നത്. ഈ അനുഗ്രഹങ്ങളോട് ഏത് വിധമാണ് പ്രതികരിച്ചതെന്നതിനെപ്പറ്റി അല്ലാഹുവിന്റെ ചോദ്യം ചെയ്യലില്‍ നിന്ന് നമുക്ക് ഒഴിഞ്ഞുമാറാനാവില്ല.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma latus'alunna yawma-idhin ʿani al-naʿīmi ","translations":["Then","surely you will be asked","that Day","about","the pleasures","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","latus'alunna","yawma-idhin","ʿani","al-naʿīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1580],[2,1580,3839],[3,3839,5159],[4,5159,5639],[5,5639,11874]]}}],"chapter":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur","Chapter At-Takathur","Takathur","Surah Takathur","Chapter Takathur","At Takathur","Surah At Takathur","Chapter At Takathur","Surah 102","Chapter 102","The Rivalry","التكاثر"],"version":{"key":"malayalam_kunhi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ml","version":"1.0.3","last_update":1622322000,"title":"Malayalam translation - Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and Kanhi Muhammad","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Malayalam by Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and Kanhi Muhammad."}}